articles.author: Anna Orso
articles.title: Cherelle Parker is poised to make history as Philly’s first female mayor - The Philadelphia Inquirer
articles.description: Former City Councilmember Cherelle Parker is well-positioned to be the first female mayor of Philadelphia, one of only a few major American cities that has only ever elected men.
articles.content:
Cherelle Parker didnt once say the word woman, but she didnt need to.
